OL,5, The last time I saw Igor Girkin was    
OL,6, five years ago in the stairwell of a   
OL,7, Moscow news agency.                    
OL,9,F"Would you consider giving me an       
OL,10,Finterview?" I asked. "No," he replied  
OL,11,Fsharply and scurried away.             
OL,13,FI saw him again today. No stairwell.   
OL,14,FThis time, Girkin was in a caged dock  
OL,15,Fsurrounded by police in the Moscow City
OL,16,FCourt.                                 
OL,18,FAlong with other media we were allowed 
OL,19,Fin to film him for just one minute     
OL,20,Fbefore the end of his trial.           
